1
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:40,980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

2
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,990
=Episode 39=

3
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:02,940
Xiaoxiao.

4
00:02:38,070 --> 00:02:38,910
Thank heavens.

5
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:40,460
You're still alive.

6
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:43,350
I don't want you to die.

7
00:02:49,580 --> 00:02:50,420
Got it.

8
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:09,300
In the end, I still died

9
00:03:09,300 --> 00:03:10,620
for the one I love.

10
00:03:40,950 --> 00:03:41,790
Farewell,

11
00:03:45,300 --> 00:03:46,140
Yan Ke.

12
00:04:47,590 --> 00:04:48,620
It's Miss He.

13
00:04:48,670 --> 00:04:49,510
- Yes.
- Yes.

14
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:51,470
Miss He won the fight.

15
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,300
Blast it!

16
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:54,170
We won!

17
00:04:54,230 --> 00:04:55,860
We made it out alive!

18
00:04:58,380 --> 00:04:59,420
We won!

19
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:01,470
We won!

20
00:05:01,550 --> 00:05:02,400
We won!

21
00:05:02,470 --> 00:05:03,550
We won!

22
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:09,470
We won.

23
00:05:11,110 --> 00:05:12,350
We won.

24
00:05:14,420 --> 00:05:15,910
We won.

25
00:05:16,030 --> 00:05:19,590
We won!

26
00:05:19,990 --> 00:05:21,150
We won.

27
00:05:22,550 --> 00:05:23,390
Xiaoxiao.

28
00:05:30,670 --> 00:05:31,510
Xiaoxiao.

29
00:05:51,590 --> 00:05:52,430
(It is Xu.)

30
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:05,230
Did you come to kill me?

31
00:06:05,710 --> 00:06:06,623
North Chong has fallen.

32
00:06:07,820 --> 00:06:08,990
The Cangshen you believed in

33
00:06:11,150 --> 00:06:12,230
was never real.

34
00:06:13,260 --> 00:06:14,790
Yan Ke, who gave you power,

35
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:17,150
has met annihilation as well.

36
00:06:18,350 --> 00:06:19,380
Even the North soldiers

37
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,230
who trusted only you

38
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:22,500
were dead because of you.

39
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:25,060
You have nothing left now.

40
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:27,260
Nonsense.

41
00:06:28,350 --> 00:06:29,990
I did not cause their deaths.

42
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:32,940
You killed them.

43
00:06:35,180 --> 00:06:36,910
I'll avenge them on you.

44
00:07:24,670 --> 00:07:26,470
I thought I was going to lose you.

45
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:31,020
No.

46
00:07:32,710 --> 00:07:34,150
You will never lose me.

47
00:08:02,550 --> 00:08:03,390
Xu.

48
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:04,870
Xiaoxiao.

49
00:08:05,910 --> 00:08:06,750
I'm back.

50
00:08:44,190 --> 00:08:45,330
The Chong people's privileges

51
00:08:45,341 --> 00:08:46,670
in the 17 Prefectures are revoked.

52
00:08:47,470 --> 00:08:48,756
All lands and houses they seized

53
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:50,990
must be returned
to Great Liang's people.

54
00:08:51,590 --> 00:08:52,540
Within Liang's borders,

55
00:08:53,140 --> 00:08:54,740
all people are born equal.

56
00:08:55,140 --> 00:08:56,430
None shall serve another people.

57
00:08:56,766 --> 00:08:57,899
People's will shall be loyal

58
00:08:58,110 --> 00:08:58,950
to His Majesty,

59
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,646
(Decree)
as it should be.

60
00:09:01,110 --> 00:09:02,023
This is hereby claimed.

61
00:09:02,190 --> 00:09:04,470
Wonderful. Wonderful.

62
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:08,420
(Rice Shop)

63
00:09:08,430 --> 00:09:09,270
The Chong foe!

64
00:09:52,990 --> 00:09:54,950
Great Ancestor.

65
00:10:13,710 --> 00:10:14,900
I have not failed your trust.

66
00:10:16,470 --> 00:10:17,540
I've retaken all

67
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:18,430
of our lost lands.

68
00:10:19,430 --> 00:10:20,663
I now return the military tally

69
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:21,770
and the marshal's seal

70
00:10:22,710 --> 00:10:23,620
to His Majesty.

71
00:10:24,190 --> 00:10:26,310
You've done an unprecedented feat.

72
00:10:26,780 --> 00:10:27,620
That is high merit.

73
00:10:28,110 --> 00:10:28,950
The people of Liang

74
00:10:29,230 --> 00:10:30,110
will remember it.

75
00:10:39,140 --> 00:10:40,740
You gave up military power so easily?

76
00:10:41,310 --> 00:10:42,740
I never meant to hold an army.

77
00:10:43,673 --> 00:10:44,740
Now that the 17 Prefectures

78
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:45,620
have been recovered,

79
00:10:46,710 --> 00:10:47,990
I should return military power

80
00:10:48,110 --> 00:10:49,070
to His Majesty.

81
00:11:13,950 --> 00:11:15,109
How much time do I have left?

82
00:11:21,470 --> 00:11:22,380
Just tell me.

83
00:11:28,190 --> 00:11:30,020
When you stop dodging your medicine,

84
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,310
I will tell you.

85
00:11:53,180 --> 00:12:00,540
(Liang)

86
00:12:05,310 --> 00:12:06,190
Is he asleep?

87
00:12:09,590 --> 00:12:11,190
Duan Xu is not doing well.

88
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:12,740
He...

89
00:12:14,740 --> 00:12:15,950
If he really leaves,

90
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:18,470
what will you do?

91
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:28,830
I still have much to do.

92
00:12:30,470 --> 00:12:32,660
Jiang Ai is watching the Void for me,

93
00:12:33,710 --> 00:12:34,900
but her heart is not in it.

94
00:12:35,470 --> 00:12:36,830
In time, she will return it to me.

95
00:12:37,830 --> 00:12:38,670
Also, Chenying

96
00:12:39,310 --> 00:12:40,740
absorbed the Spirits Lantern's power

97
00:12:40,740 --> 00:12:41,580
and became a spirit.

98
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:43,660
His obsession is to protect.

99
00:12:44,310 --> 00:12:45,500
If he is willing,

100
00:12:46,190 --> 00:12:47,350
perhaps he can take over

101
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,190
my place soon.

102
00:12:50,830 --> 00:12:51,740
I'm not talking

103
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:53,140
about the Sovereign.

104
00:12:54,860 --> 00:12:55,900
I'm talking

105
00:12:58,350 --> 00:12:59,540
about you.

106
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:17,460
I don't know.

107
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:22,860
Perhaps when that day comes,

108
00:13:24,350 --> 00:13:25,230
I will know.

109
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:43,860
Right now, whenever I think

110
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:46,900
that Duan Xu may leave me,

111
00:13:48,710 --> 00:13:49,550
I feel

112
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,740
as if time might vanish

113
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:54,780
into thin air.

114
00:13:58,190 --> 00:13:59,780
I can see so many things

115
00:13:59,780 --> 00:14:00,710
waiting for me to do,

116
00:14:05,020 --> 00:14:06,540
yet I can't see myself.

117
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:29,620
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

118
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:39,900
Simu, you are back.

119
00:14:41,350 --> 00:14:42,230
Who is this?

120
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:45,020
This is my brother, Chenying.

121
00:14:45,566 --> 00:14:47,045
The Spirits Lantern made him a spirit.

122
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:47,950
He's still very weak.

123
00:14:48,350 --> 00:14:50,260
Lady Jiang Ai, please watch over him.

124
00:14:51,110 --> 00:14:51,950
Also,

125
00:14:52,020 --> 00:14:52,880
please oversee

126
00:14:52,900 --> 00:14:54,140
the Void for a while longer.

127
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:00,740
With Lady Jiang Ai here,

128
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:02,460
don't worry.

129
00:15:12,660 --> 00:15:14,470
What obsession brought you here?

130
00:15:16,310 --> 00:15:18,430
I want to protect Xu and Xiaoxiao.

131
00:15:19,230 --> 00:15:21,230
I kept thinking they had not made peace,

132
00:15:21,710 --> 00:15:22,660
and their wishes

133
00:15:22,860 --> 00:15:23,900
have yet to come true.

134
00:15:24,990 --> 00:15:26,260
I had to see them again.

135
00:15:27,020 --> 00:15:27,860
And I had to

136
00:15:27,990 --> 00:15:29,350
make their wishes come true.

137
00:15:30,710 --> 00:15:31,570
Then

138
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:32,860
I really saw them again.

139
00:15:33,780 --> 00:15:34,620
How lucky.

140
00:15:36,470 --> 00:15:37,500
At such a young age,

141
00:15:37,500 --> 00:15:38,860
you carry such heavy sorrow,

142
00:15:38,860 --> 00:15:40,140
yet you count yourself lucky.

143
00:15:42,380 --> 00:15:43,230
I'm not lucky.

144
00:15:44,590 --> 00:15:45,740
Xu is gravely ill.

145
00:15:46,660 --> 00:15:48,110
Xiaoxiao is hurting too.

146
00:15:49,380 --> 00:15:50,860
But I can't help in the least.

147
00:15:52,860 --> 00:15:53,700
Lady Jiang Ai,

148
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:56,110
if Xu is gone...

149
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:02,780
(Tomb of He Yicheng and Siwei)

150
00:16:02,780 --> 00:16:03,620
Old man,

151
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:06,380
your grudge has been settled.

152
00:16:09,590 --> 00:16:10,430
Are you pleased?

153
00:16:21,230 --> 00:16:22,260
It's been over 400 years.

154
00:16:25,230 --> 00:16:26,740
I am older than you two now.

155
00:16:29,860 --> 00:16:30,700
From now on,

156
00:16:32,590 --> 00:16:34,190
you may have one more neighbor.

157
00:16:35,620 --> 00:16:36,500
After he passes,

158
00:16:38,050 --> 00:16:38,900
I plan to lay him

159
00:16:38,900 --> 00:16:39,990
to rest beside you two.

160
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:51,350
After you left, I swore

161
00:16:54,350 --> 00:16:56,020
I'd never be left behind again,

162
00:16:57,780 --> 00:16:59,350
and I'd be the one who leaves first.

163
00:16:59,420 --> 00:17:03,340
(Tomb of He Yicheng and Siwei)

164
00:17:03,710 --> 00:17:05,340
But I repeat my mistake again.

165
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:10,060
I gave him the right

166
00:17:11,460 --> 00:17:12,300
to leave me

167
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:13,670
before I do.

168
00:17:16,780 --> 00:17:17,780
One day,

169
00:17:20,150 --> 00:17:22,060
I suppose it will break my heart.

170
00:17:27,870 --> 00:17:28,710
And now,

171
00:17:29,670 --> 00:17:30,780
I find myself thinking

172
00:17:32,045 --> 00:17:33,939
that if he left me and vanished
from this world

173
00:17:33,950 --> 00:17:35,300
50 years from now,

174
00:17:37,260 --> 00:17:38,100
it wouldn't be

175
00:17:38,100 --> 00:17:39,470
so impossible to bear.

176
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:47,390
But I've known him for only 7 years.

177
00:17:51,230 --> 00:17:52,630
It's too short.

178
00:17:55,470 --> 00:17:56,780
Truly, far too short.

179
00:18:17,870 --> 00:18:20,060
But there is no helping it,

180
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:22,340
is there?

181
00:18:48,900 --> 00:18:53,300
(Youzhou)

182
00:19:00,820 --> 00:19:01,660
All is settled now.

183
00:19:02,390 --> 00:19:03,230
Today, I shall drink

184
00:19:03,950 --> 00:19:04,790
with all of you.

185
00:19:05,260 --> 00:19:06,390
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

186
00:19:13,710 --> 00:19:15,260
I truly never imagined

187
00:19:15,740 --> 00:19:18,020
that after such a brutal battle,

188
00:19:18,580 --> 00:19:19,910
not only did we all survive,

189
00:19:20,230 --> 00:19:22,190
but we also reclaimed
the 17 Prefectures.

190
00:19:22,910 --> 00:19:24,940
My life is worth it.

191
00:19:25,060 --> 00:19:25,900
Worth it indeed.

192
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:27,910
Han.

193
00:19:27,990 --> 00:19:28,830
Qingsheng.

194
00:19:31,390 --> 00:19:32,665
- Here.
- That we could reclaim

195
00:19:32,676 --> 00:19:33,630
the 17 Prefectures

196
00:19:33,870 --> 00:19:34,780
feels like a dream.

197
00:19:39,430 --> 00:19:41,180
- I still remember
- Marshal Duan.

198
00:19:41,630 --> 00:19:42,470
we entered Liangzhou.

199
00:19:44,230 --> 00:19:45,540
Back then, you even suspected

200
00:19:45,540 --> 00:19:46,380
I was a spy.

201
00:19:48,150 --> 00:19:49,089
Now that I think of it,

202
00:19:49,100 --> 00:19:50,060
he did look like a spy.

203
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:52,030
Come on.

204
00:19:52,470 --> 00:19:53,340
Cheers.

205
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:54,180
Let's drink.

206
00:19:58,740 --> 00:19:59,580
Marshal Duan,

207
00:20:00,100 --> 00:20:01,870
I heard you returned

208
00:20:01,870 --> 00:20:02,710
the marshal's seal.

209
00:20:04,580 --> 00:20:06,500
If you don't want to be the Marshal,

210
00:20:06,910 --> 00:20:08,630
give that seal to me.

211
00:20:08,910 --> 00:20:10,260
I will take the post for you.

212
00:20:10,260 --> 00:20:11,390
Would that not be just fine?

213
00:20:11,780 --> 00:20:12,620
General Wu,

214
00:20:12,780 --> 00:20:13,820
as I told you long ago,

215
00:20:14,430 --> 00:20:15,780
if you chased office in Nandu,

216
00:20:16,470 --> 00:20:17,710
you'd be done for.

217
00:20:19,060 --> 00:20:20,100
Marshal Duan is right.

218
00:20:21,580 --> 00:20:22,710
Right about what?

219
00:20:23,910 --> 00:20:25,670
I was only joking.

220
00:20:26,190 --> 00:20:27,150
I'd never be an official

221
00:20:27,150 --> 00:20:28,190
in Nandu.

222
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:29,630
I won this land back

223
00:20:29,630 --> 00:20:31,260
with my life.

224
00:20:31,710 --> 00:20:32,580
I wouldn't rest easy

225
00:20:32,580 --> 00:20:33,670
leaving it to others.

226
00:20:35,020 --> 00:20:36,540
Han, say a few words.

227
00:20:38,390 --> 00:20:39,430
General Wu is right.

228
00:20:40,630 --> 00:20:42,100
I've grown used to the frontier.

229
00:20:42,910 --> 00:20:43,896
I can't go anywhere else.

230
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:50,340
Come, come.

231
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:51,710
So you've all decided

232
00:20:52,870 --> 00:20:53,710
to stay here?

233
00:20:55,630 --> 00:20:56,470
That's right.

234
00:20:56,820 --> 00:20:57,670
We'll stay to guard

235
00:20:57,910 --> 00:20:58,750
the frontier.

236
00:21:03,060 --> 00:21:03,900
I'll go

237
00:21:04,670 --> 00:21:05,510
where Meng Wan goes.

238
00:21:09,100 --> 00:21:10,190
Han and I

239
00:21:10,390 --> 00:21:11,390
will stand with you two.

240
00:21:15,190 --> 00:21:16,060
Xu, what about you?

241
00:21:43,390 --> 00:21:44,710
The 17 Prefectures are back.

242
00:21:46,190 --> 00:21:47,030
My wish is fulfilled.

243
00:21:48,780 --> 00:21:50,580
Simu and I will wander the realm

244
00:21:52,060 --> 00:21:52,900
and never return.

245
00:22:01,190 --> 00:22:02,030
Xu,

246
00:22:03,780 --> 00:22:05,020
are you truly leaving?

247
00:22:20,060 --> 00:22:21,020
Though we part,

248
00:22:24,580 --> 00:22:25,580
we still share the wind.

249
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:40,340
(Liang)

250
00:23:41,950 --> 00:23:43,540
Your wishes have all come true.

251
00:23:44,430 --> 00:23:45,870
What will you do now?

252
00:23:48,500 --> 00:23:49,340
Simu,

253
00:23:50,910 --> 00:23:51,910
I had a dream last night.

254
00:23:56,500 --> 00:23:57,340
In that dream,

255
00:23:58,230 --> 00:23:59,376
we lived a life of seclusion.

256
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:01,296
One cottage, two souls,

257
00:24:02,557 --> 00:24:03,790
three meals, and four seasons.

258
00:24:06,670 --> 00:24:07,510
Seeds in spring,

259
00:24:08,150 --> 00:24:08,990
rain in summer,

260
00:24:09,710 --> 00:24:10,710
chrysanthemums in autumn,

261
00:24:11,470 --> 00:24:12,310
and snow in winter.

262
00:24:15,430 --> 00:24:16,340
Year after year,

263
00:24:17,670 --> 00:24:19,100
we lived a quiet, ordinary life.

264
00:24:20,230 --> 00:24:22,790
♪With the east wind♪

265
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:28,250
♪In the season at its fullest♪

266
00:24:28,260 --> 00:24:29,366
I want to return to our home

267
00:24:33,190 --> 00:24:34,030
with you.

268
00:24:34,690 --> 00:24:37,500
♪The old night♪

269
00:24:39,450 --> 00:24:46,410
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

270
00:24:47,260 --> 00:24:48,100
All right.

271
00:24:50,390 --> 00:24:53,910
♪Savoring wine and graceful dances♪

272
00:24:54,090 --> 00:25:00,910
♪Let me love with all my heart
in youthful grace♪

273
00:25:01,280 --> 00:25:09,330
♪With light, carefree words,
still shining bright♪

274
00:25:09,670 --> 00:25:12,570
♪With you by my side♪

275
00:25:16,470 --> 00:25:17,780
It's truly good to be home.

276
00:25:18,870 --> 00:25:20,020
This is my home.

277
00:25:21,390 --> 00:25:22,383
That was a gift from me,

278
00:25:23,540 --> 00:25:24,630
along with myself.

279
00:25:26,550 --> 00:25:27,616
What would you like to eat?

280
00:25:27,836 --> 00:25:29,069
I'll take you to get some food.

281
00:25:29,820 --> 00:25:30,660
Simu,

282
00:25:31,150 --> 00:25:31,990
let's have fish.

283
00:25:31,990 --> 00:25:36,060
♪If you'd let me know how to tell♪

284
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:38,230
I don't know how to cook fish.

285
00:25:38,230 --> 00:25:39,080
You chose

286
00:25:39,090 --> 00:25:40,190
such tricky ingredients.

287
00:25:40,190 --> 00:25:41,540
Isn't it enough that I can?

288
00:25:42,260 --> 00:25:43,580
We're having a full fish banquet.

289
00:25:46,020 --> 00:25:53,310
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

290
00:25:54,340 --> 00:25:55,580
It doesn't seem willing.

291
00:25:55,710 --> 00:25:56,670
What a slippery fish.

292
00:25:57,470 --> 00:25:58,310
Simu,

293
00:25:58,710 --> 00:25:59,550
help me scoop it up.

294
00:26:01,470 --> 00:26:02,310
Let's give it a try.

295
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:07,690
♪In youthful grace♪

296
00:26:07,930 --> 00:26:10,960
♪With light, carefree words♪

297
00:26:12,780 --> 00:26:13,620
Simu,

298
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:16,630
I like being with you.

299
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:22,590
♪A pot of wine in fleeting dreams♪

300
00:26:24,250 --> 00:26:32,620
♪A brief life dares seek eternity♪

301
00:26:33,410 --> 00:26:39,410
♪Borrow one lovely dream;
let me savor this fleeting joy♪

302
00:26:39,870 --> 00:26:40,710
Your Grace,

303
00:26:41,910 --> 00:26:42,780
do you still like

304
00:26:43,540 --> 00:26:45,020
my skull as you did

305
00:26:46,230 --> 00:26:47,430
back then?

306
00:26:49,780 --> 00:26:50,620
Yes.

307
00:26:51,820 --> 00:26:52,780
I want to remember you,

308
00:26:54,630 --> 00:26:55,470
your smile,

309
00:26:56,990 --> 00:26:57,870
your scent,

310
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:00,380
your colors,

311
00:27:01,910 --> 00:27:02,870
and this moment.

312
00:27:07,320 --> 00:27:09,890
♪To what home shall I return♪

313
00:27:10,020 --> 00:27:10,860
Great Ancestor...

314
00:27:14,340 --> 00:27:15,260
Let's go.

315
00:27:15,260 --> 00:27:16,100
Stop there.

316
00:27:17,630 --> 00:27:18,470
Come here.

317
00:27:20,780 --> 00:27:21,740
Great Ancestor,

318
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:23,060
spare my life.

319
00:27:23,670 --> 00:27:24,510
I...

320
00:27:24,670 --> 00:27:25,710
I have just recovered.

321
00:27:26,100 --> 00:27:27,630
My eyes still have excessive heat,

322
00:27:28,230 --> 00:27:29,260
so they're not so sharp.

323
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:31,580
I saw nothing at all.

324
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:35,150
I came to deliver medicine
to General Duan.

325
00:27:36,150 --> 00:27:38,100
I brought all of these

326
00:27:38,100 --> 00:27:38,940
from Starhaven Sect.

327
00:27:41,990 --> 00:27:43,190
I am no longer a general.

328
00:27:44,230 --> 00:27:45,150
Since you're here,

329
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:46,950
stay for a simple meal.

330
00:27:47,190 --> 00:27:48,030
No, no.

331
00:27:48,430 --> 00:27:50,430
I won't disturb you. Goodbye.

332
00:27:50,470 --> 00:27:51,580
I'll cook today.

333
00:27:52,710 --> 00:27:53,950
Don't you want a taste?

334
00:28:09,710 --> 00:28:10,550
Great Ancestor,

335
00:28:11,300 --> 00:28:13,470
you aren't treating him like a patient,

336
00:28:15,580 --> 00:28:16,820
nor me like a person.

337
00:28:17,740 --> 00:28:19,470
Then starve yourself.

338
00:28:46,260 --> 00:28:47,100
Is it good?

339
00:29:03,060 --> 00:29:03,900
I'll go check on him.

340
00:29:10,020 --> 00:29:11,620
Ziji, sit down and eat.

341
00:29:26,060 --> 00:29:27,020
It's not that bad.

342
00:29:28,260 --> 00:29:29,300
It tastes fine to me.

343
00:29:44,500 --> 00:29:45,340
What's wrong?

344
00:29:46,580 --> 00:29:47,420
Look, look.

345
00:29:47,710 --> 00:29:48,820
It's not that bad, huh?

346
00:29:49,390 --> 00:29:50,340
I only threw up my food.

347
00:29:50,340 --> 00:29:51,320
You're coughing up blood.

348
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:53,580
How is it?

349
00:29:53,820 --> 00:29:54,800
Do you have any medicine?

350
00:29:55,230 --> 00:29:56,296
- I have some.
- I'm fine.

351
00:29:58,340 --> 00:29:59,280
Which kind do you want?

352
00:30:00,260 --> 00:30:01,100
I'm fine.

353
00:30:02,710 --> 00:30:03,550
However,

354
00:30:06,470 --> 00:30:07,670
I do have one favor to ask.

355
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:10,420
What do you want?

356
00:30:14,580 --> 00:30:15,420
Come here.

357
00:30:16,870 --> 00:30:17,710
Come closer.

358
00:30:25,190 --> 00:30:26,030
What?

359
00:30:26,470 --> 00:30:27,310
Duan Shunxi.

360
00:30:29,020 --> 00:30:29,860
Duan Shunxi,

361
00:30:30,630 --> 00:30:31,990
I've never

362
00:30:31,990 --> 00:30:32,830
wronged you.

363
00:30:32,840 --> 00:30:33,680
Why must you make me

364
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:34,560
await my end

365
00:30:34,560 --> 00:30:35,450
before Great Ancestor?

366
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:50,870
Everything in this world

367
00:30:51,430 --> 00:30:52,870
will one day fade away.

368
00:30:54,300 --> 00:30:55,230
Your Grace,

369
00:30:55,990 --> 00:30:56,896
why force him to stay?

370
00:30:59,300 --> 00:31:00,340
This is his fate.

371
00:31:01,300 --> 00:31:02,150
None of your business.

372
00:31:10,060 --> 00:31:11,190
As the Sovereign of the Void,

373
00:31:12,260 --> 00:31:13,670
you can't stay in the Mortal World.

374
00:31:15,100 --> 00:31:16,100
Go back soon.

375
00:31:17,470 --> 00:31:18,950
Then how much longer will you stay

376
00:31:18,950 --> 00:31:19,910
in this Mortal World,

377
00:31:21,670 --> 00:31:22,510
Immortal?

378
00:31:42,430 --> 00:31:43,270
Duan Shunxi,

379
00:31:44,990 --> 00:31:46,540
you'll leave Great Ancestor.

380
00:31:47,780 --> 00:31:48,820
Aren't you sad?

381
00:31:53,950 --> 00:31:54,790
In all my life,

382
00:31:57,150 --> 00:31:58,540
from first love to my dying day,

383
00:32:01,190 --> 00:32:02,780
I have only loved one girl.

384
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:08,190
I count myself lucky.

385
00:32:10,910 --> 00:32:11,750
Now,

386
00:32:13,710 --> 00:32:15,580
I don't want my last days in sorrow.

387
00:32:21,390 --> 00:32:22,230
Still,

388
00:32:22,670 --> 00:32:23,990
perhaps when I die,

389
00:32:26,540 --> 00:32:27,630
I'll cling to her and weep.

390
00:33:12,470 --> 00:33:13,310
After I am gone,

391
00:33:14,670 --> 00:33:15,580
will you grieve for me?

392
00:33:17,470 --> 00:33:18,740
Will you hold me and weep too?

393
00:33:25,910 --> 00:33:27,020
All these years,

394
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:30,670
whenever my death is mentioned,

395
00:33:30,780 --> 00:33:31,990
you say nothing.

396
00:33:33,390 --> 00:33:34,230
How absurd.

397
00:33:35,260 --> 00:33:36,430
What are you running from?

398
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:39,230
Didn't your kind

399
00:33:39,910 --> 00:33:41,670
set this brief fate

400
00:33:42,020 --> 00:33:43,100
for the Hejia lineage,

401
00:33:44,260 --> 00:33:45,230
Immortal?

402
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:50,980
You stayed by my side

403
00:33:50,980 --> 00:33:52,260
and read mortals for years.

404
00:33:53,060 --> 00:33:53,900
Now,

405
00:33:54,060 --> 00:33:56,230
do you think your kind was wrong?

406
00:33:58,190 --> 00:33:59,470
Immortals don't err.

407
00:34:00,630 --> 00:34:01,870
Even mortals' right and wrong

408
00:34:02,540 --> 00:34:03,670
are set by immortals.

409
00:34:07,710 --> 00:34:08,550
Yes.

410
00:34:08,950 --> 00:34:09,790
How very clever.

411
00:34:10,870 --> 00:34:12,140
How could immortals be wrong?

412
00:34:13,910 --> 00:34:14,950
Then why did you create

413
00:34:14,950 --> 00:34:15,870
this order

414
00:34:15,870 --> 00:34:16,710
in the first place?

415
00:34:17,870 --> 00:34:19,470
To keep the world in balance

416
00:34:20,390 --> 00:34:21,910
and secure happiness for most.

417
00:34:22,020 --> 00:34:22,860
So,

418
00:34:23,220 --> 00:34:24,060
you have been using

419
00:34:24,060 --> 00:34:24,990
our kindness.

420
00:34:25,750 --> 00:34:26,590
We have upheld

421
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:27,660
the happiness of the many.

422
00:34:27,990 --> 00:34:29,060
Yet we have no choice

423
00:34:29,060 --> 00:34:30,350
but to suffer for it.

424
00:34:30,790 --> 00:34:31,990
You dress it up in noble words

425
00:34:31,990 --> 00:34:32,950
while tormenting us.

426
00:34:34,310 --> 00:34:35,456
Don't you see your arrogance?

427
00:34:37,830 --> 00:34:38,670
That is

428
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:40,750
why I have come here.

429
00:34:43,500 --> 00:34:45,310
If you still see no fault in yourself,

430
00:34:46,310 --> 00:34:47,660
go back.

431
00:34:49,990 --> 00:34:50,830
Ziji,

432
00:34:51,580 --> 00:34:52,500
to speak plainly,

433
00:34:54,350 --> 00:34:55,790
I am tired of this game.

434
00:35:01,750 --> 00:35:02,870
(Ten years by your side)

435
00:35:03,990 --> 00:35:04,830
(until this day.)

436
00:35:07,540 --> 00:35:08,470
(Immortal,)

437
00:35:10,750 --> 00:35:11,750
(will you save me?)

438
00:35:14,730 --> 00:35:18,350
♪In silence, I gaze at you♪

439
00:35:18,550 --> 00:35:22,280
♪My hand hangs and then falls♪

440
00:35:22,630 --> 00:35:26,190
♪Let what stays unsaid pass♪

441
00:35:27,030 --> 00:35:30,440
♪Why torture each other like this?♪

442
00:35:30,720 --> 00:35:33,990
♪My wish might be♪

443
00:35:35,060 --> 00:35:35,900
Ziji,

444
00:35:38,100 --> 00:35:39,270
you grabbed me.

445
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:44,100
♪They fade like a dream♪

446
00:35:45,750 --> 00:35:49,610
♪Daylight fades into ash♪

447
00:35:50,540 --> 00:35:52,259
(It's been over a month
since your letter.)

448
00:35:53,220 --> 00:35:55,020
(Are you and Miss He both well?)

449
00:35:59,100 --> 00:35:59,950
(Somehow,)

450
00:36:00,910 --> 00:36:02,270
(I often dream)

451
00:36:02,270 --> 00:36:04,220
(of our childhood days in Daizhou.)

452
00:36:04,540 --> 00:36:06,820
(Daizhou)

453
00:36:08,470 --> 00:36:14,340
♪Collapse piece by piece♪

454
00:36:16,700 --> 00:36:19,550
♪I hate that I hesitated♪

455
00:36:19,550 --> 00:36:21,910
(Yet old days will fade like mist.)

456
00:36:21,910 --> 00:36:24,280
(Erudite and Determined)

457
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:26,270
♪Leaving all behind♪

458
00:36:26,310 --> 00:36:27,950
(I have found what I wish to do.)

459
00:36:28,580 --> 00:36:29,620
(For now, all is well.)

460
00:36:32,870 --> 00:36:34,700
(Though the moon may wax and wane,)

461
00:36:35,790 --> 00:36:37,310
(I still wish that you and Miss He)

462
00:36:37,620 --> 00:36:38,740
(can be as full as the moon)

463
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:40,790
(and live a happy life.)

464
00:36:41,910 --> 00:36:43,950
(Your sister, Jingyuan, respectfully)

465
00:37:02,860 --> 00:37:06,020
(Your sister, Jingyuan, respectfully)

466
00:37:07,130 --> 00:37:10,640
♪Let memories drift away♪

467
00:37:11,010 --> 00:37:13,680
♪Alone, I gather them up♪

468
00:37:13,890 --> 00:37:18,340
♪Like petals in the spring sun♪

469
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:22,200
♪Till the past falls still again♪

470
00:37:22,560 --> 00:37:26,120
♪And turns to clear daylight♪

471
00:37:26,310 --> 00:37:34,700
♪The wind returns with my dreams♪

472
00:37:56,390 --> 00:37:57,680
Will you send Jingyuan a reply?

473
00:38:00,470 --> 00:38:02,060
She's found what she wants to do

474
00:38:03,270 --> 00:38:04,430
and started a new life.

475
00:38:05,660 --> 00:38:07,060
I won't give her more to worry over.

476
00:38:13,750 --> 00:38:14,590
Jingyuan mentioned

477
00:38:14,590 --> 00:38:15,830
those days back in Daizhou.

478
00:38:20,020 --> 00:38:20,860
I think

479
00:38:22,990 --> 00:38:24,310
she cared for Xianye.

480
00:38:27,731 --> 00:38:28,965
If the time they spent together

481
00:38:28,976 --> 00:38:29,670
had been longer,

482
00:38:31,870 --> 00:38:32,710
perhaps...

483
00:38:44,399 --> 00:38:45,512
Maybe this is for the best.

484
00:38:48,430 --> 00:38:49,830
She should soon forget

485
00:38:52,430 --> 00:38:53,950
a brief, hazy memory.

486
00:38:57,390 --> 00:38:58,500
How could she forget?

487
00:39:00,140 --> 00:39:00,980
She will not.

488
00:39:08,470 --> 00:39:10,180
Jingyuan wished us full as the moon.

489
00:39:12,433 --> 00:39:14,079
Yet we're here,
and the full moon is not.

490
00:39:16,953 --> 00:39:17,950
It's been so long since I

491
00:39:17,950 --> 00:39:18,993
admired the moon with you.

492
00:39:21,790 --> 00:39:22,790
The Mid-Autumn Festival

493
00:39:24,470 --> 00:39:25,500
is too far away.

494
00:39:26,986 --> 00:39:28,492
If you want to celebrate the festival,

495
00:39:28,620 --> 00:39:29,470
we can do it anytime.

496
00:39:31,060 --> 00:39:31,900
But if you want

497
00:39:33,430 --> 00:39:34,620
to admire the moon...

498
00:39:39,350 --> 00:39:40,190
Wait for a moment.

499
00:41:27,910 --> 00:41:28,750
Simu.

500
00:41:30,897 --> 00:41:32,917
The moonlight beneath the sun
is beautiful, right?

501
00:41:37,700 --> 00:41:38,540
Do you like it?

502
00:41:39,660 --> 00:41:40,500
I do.

503
00:41:42,060 --> 00:41:43,020
I always do.

504
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:16,010
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

505
00:42:16,340 --> 00:42:20,590
♪Light encountered shadow♪

506
00:42:21,950 --> 00:42:27,320
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

507
00:42:27,620 --> 00:42:32,220
♪The unbreakable fate♪

508
00:42:33,310 --> 00:42:35,150
♪Suddenly cracked♪

509
00:42:47,360 --> 00:42:52,800
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

510
00:42:52,980 --> 00:42:57,310
♪Light encountered shadow♪

511
00:42:58,680 --> 00:43:04,070
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

512
00:43:04,300 --> 00:43:08,240
♪The unbreakable fate♪

513
00:43:10,010 --> 00:43:11,900
♪Suddenly cracked♪

514
00:43:14,560 --> 00:43:17,720
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

515
00:43:17,720 --> 00:43:20,250
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

516
00:43:20,250 --> 00:43:25,770
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

517
00:43:25,770 --> 00:43:29,010
♪Following fate's guidance♪

518
00:43:29,010 --> 00:43:33,870
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

519
00:43:34,210 --> 00:43:37,230
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

520
00:43:37,230 --> 00:43:40,050
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

521
00:43:40,310 --> 00:43:42,840
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

522
00:43:42,840 --> 00:43:48,260
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

523
00:43:48,430 --> 00:43:51,500
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

524
00:43:51,660 --> 00:43:56,560
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

525
00:43:56,770 --> 00:44:00,240
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

